# Monorepo Rules

For package creation: `.ai/skills/create-package.md`
For app creation: `.ai/skills/create-app.md`

## Key conventions
- Package scope: `@turbo/*`
- All packages use `"type": "module"`
- Exports defined via `package.json` `exports` field
- Shared configs in `tooling/*`
- Deep reference: `.agents/skills/turborepo/`
